FBIS4-36227 "drnes109_j_94001" FBIS-NES-94-109 Daily Report 6 Jun 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Sanaa Agrees to Cease-Fire Beginning Midnight 6 Jun Sanaa Agrees to Cease-Fire Beginning Midnight 6 Jun NC0606143694 Paris AFP in English 1429 GMT 6 Jun 94 NC0606143694 Paris AFP English BFN [Text] Sanaa, June 6 (AFP) -- The Yemeni Government has agreed to observe a ceasefire from midnight (2100 GMT) on Monday [6 June], Foreign Minister Muhammad Basindwah announced. He told reporters the government had informed UN Secretary General Butrus Butrus-Ghali and Arab League Chief 'Ismat 'Abd-al-Majid that "a ceasefire will start from midnight tonight."
